Dialogue: Emit PDN, ammo-ct xet.

I hear you've found
some new housing.
Again with the head shot!

Maybe next year they'll
let me carry sacks!
Neuro-what?

Are you certain this
neurolink is on tight?

What comes after white
and black? Red, I say!
Red!? Don't you mean blue!?

What evils would bring
together two primals, a
behemoth, and a bomb!?

Er......
Can I have three guesses?

Now where did I put that
clockwork Doomtrain?

Abandon all hope,
ye who enter here...
Oh, I'm only kidding!

What!? Did you say some-
thing!? I can't hear you!
I need my daily dose of minions...
Ah, such adorable violence...
Get away!
Let's play pirates an' planks!
Calm down, you!
Shut your mouth!
What's that!?
Got somethin' to say!?
Bunch of ne'er-do-wells...
Lemoncakes, I'm scared...
We should be fine over here.
Never let me go!
Pick up your garbage!
Hold yer damn tongue!
Show me yer moves!
Ye got some gall!
I'm lovin' it!
How pretty!
If it's you...
Godsdamn, that smarts!
Blood, it's blood!
Haha!
Hehehe!
So, do you like...stuff?
Go away!
I'll never give you up!
Mwahah!
Party time, excellent!
How's thiiis!?
Come on, you can jump higher than that!
The docks are lovely today...

Overwhelming numbers!
That's the best strategy!

I'll let him think he's winning...
Then BAM! Hee hee!
She's usually such a sweet girl...
I'm very particular about my forces!
Oh? How so?
Every minion is a mandragora!

Uh...
And that helps you win?

I spent all my MGP
on you, mate.
So we better win!
Squeee!
I think we're alone now...
How horrid...
I want to get my feet wet!
I love fireworks!
I want to be an adventurer!
Hurry! I want to go scare my sister!
Can I have my costume now?
Come on, do it! I'm here! Do it now!
Where. Is. My. Costume!?
Sweets! Sweets! Sweeeeeets!
This better not be a trick!
I love me some plunder...
Too easy!

Hello again,
old friend...

...It doesn't get any easier,
does it.

It's...it's all gone.
Everything... Gone...
I have the watch!
I...I just don't...

Pull yourself together!
We'll find a way! We always do!
Something is amiss...
Eat! Eat until stomach swells!
Eenu Vanu outdoes himself again!
Let's be off, eh?
Ah, it's you.

Even a sky pirate needs
a break from excitement.
From time to time.

I'm taking aether readings.
You know, for the ghost ship!

These values...
They're different from before.
That bleedin' ship...
Rumors are our meat and mead.

Can't enjoy me drink with
this scrag yappin' in me ear...
Bah! This place is dry.

I love it when
a plan comes together!

Well...it hasn't come
together till the beast's
in me belly.

I could've sworn I forgot
to bait the trap... Oh well.
Another day's work done.

I'm so hungry, I could eat...
well, almost anything.
That smells heavenly!
Hee hee hee!
Heretic! Kinslayer!
O Halone, we beseech You!
Die, damn you, die!
Are you injured?
It's over now...
Fury be praised...

Put your back into it!
We've ten score more of
these to clear by noon!

Why don't we ever hire
anyone who can wield
cobble-laying magicks?

Pshkohhh...
Bigger! Higher!
Build, build, build!

I've a feeling I'm
going to regret taking
Lady Rowena's coin...

Your father has already
given his consent. We are
to be married on the eve
of the new moon.
Yes, my lord.

Why am I not allowed say
in mine own affairs...?

I am a woman grown, yet
Father would treat me as
if I were a swaddling babe.

You look pale, milady.
Is aught amiss?
Might I be of some assistance?
A fine gobbiemask, that is!
A fine gobbiemask, indeed!

I've come from Ul'dah
to learn the ways
of your people!
Ah... Very well, then.

You'll see, Mother.
You'll see.

Hope it's not
like last time...

When's the dragon
going to come?

But what if the baby
comes early?

What I wouldn't give to
look behind the curtain.

Slay the stinky intruders!
Ugh, the smell!

They've a trick or two
up their sleeves.
I'm sure of it.

Bah! We've the pride
of three nations.
What have they got!?

<click> <click> 
(You saw it, yes?)
(Hush. The deftarm will hear.)
I have fulfilled my duty.
<click> <click> Very good. We have your reward.
It's not gysahl greens, is it?
We've come across some news that may interest your guild.
<click> <click> Do tell. We are eager to hear it.
Well, ain't that somethin'.
Was that stone dragon always there?
The dragons permitted us to take it. A sign of parley.

Parley with dragons!? 
Ne'er thought I'd see the day!
Your procurement of firesand has arrived.
<click> <click> The Nonmind are grateful.

Gobbies finish boomstick! 
New type, more boom!

And we have nanka eggs, special for you. 
We aged them. Especially juicy.

Got a dangerous task for ye.  
Is the guild up for a challenge?
<click> <click> We do not fear the wilds.

I am a mentor, my good
fellow! And there are no
foolish questions!
Well, in that case...
That final exercise is murderous...

Someone...er...
lend me a hand?

They haven't even told
me what we're building.

Calling all prospective
engineers!

Gobbie mindfruit is ripe
for bellyfilling! Come
take a bite!

Rippling Rainlander! Crave
you gobbie clevering?

My mind is a bottomless
well waiting to be filled.

Uh... Not sure sense is
being made...but you can
have a gobbiemask!

I wonder what Lady Rowena
has in store for this place?

I heard she's thinking of
expanding her selection
of Garlean goods...

I've lived here my whole
life, yet there are so many
places I've never seen!

And I shall show you
them all, my lady.

Thank you for allowing a
caged songbird to fly free...
even if only for an afternoon.

I did naught but unhinge
the lock. It was you who
chose to spread her wings.

And still, here I am,
alighted once again on
my father's perch.

Then make this
the last time!

Meet me tonight beneath
the Architects!
Whatever should I do?

I knew from first we met
that we were meant for
each other.

Come! Let us leave all
this behind and start
our lives anew!
Yes, my love! Yes!

The baronet will wish
to know of this treachery!

Mother asked us to fetch
mutton and popotoes. She
said nothing of honey cakes.

Right! She didn't say
we couldn't buy any!
Well, that was fast.
Proceed to the next quarter!
Keep goin', keep goin'!
Brother! Pull yourself together!
Somehow I'm still alive...
You're mine!
Taste the cold steel!
I won't let you get away!
You're bold to take on the 'Cudas!
Ware those who lurk in the shadows!
Now!
Feel my blades' sting!
I-Incredible...
We've grown...too complacent...
Isn't this a bit excessive?
Have at you!
Come on, is that all you've got?

Raaargh!
I'm all fired up!
I'll blow you away!
The waves part to my cleave!
Promise me ye won't lose to that perfumed sack o' shite up ahead.

This has been very...informative.
Until next time.

黒渦は、
すべてを呑み込む！

避けねば
大怪我では済まんぞ？
でりゃあああああ！
足下がガラ空きだ！

多勢に無勢なのだ
卑怯とは言わせんぞ？
これが海賊王の荒技よ！

大砲用の火薬樽だ…
扱いには気を付けな！

Bwahahaha!
Seems like ages since I felt this alive!

Well fought. Mayhap you will
have the pleasure of
facing me one day.

You see that shadow?
Airship? Or bird?

Need to save my strength.
Haulin' treasure's hard work,
you know!

Zzz... Gold...
Lovely, glitterin' gold...
Come to stretch your wings?

Take a seat, eh?
Put your feet up.

How do they get
so damn muddy!?

A full sixmoon of toil, and I
still haven't a gil to me name!

Yet the young maid at the
tavern seems to be faring
well, I see. Heh heh.

C-Careful, my dear,
that one was a bit
below the belt...
Pow! Right in the kisser!
Fascinating...

Alchemy 101?
Are there a hundred
other such tomes?

If you need brute strength,
then I'm your girl!

The Fury aid me...
I cannot stop shaking...

Come, then, you fiends!
I'll not let my family burn!

When they come at you,
remember your drills.

Stay with me!
...Damnable dragons.
How's the Raimille lookin'?

In great shape, Captain!
Not a squeak to be heard!

Have to keep my girl
in perfect condition...

We're ready to
fly at any time!

Hmm... Odd
little bugger...

Wherefore art thou,
Inspector Cyr...
Inspector Cyr! Inspector Cyr!

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Still out and about?

The trading of tongueflaps
is of frontmost import!
A place of trading them
is of middlemost!

It's hotter than Ifrit's arse
after a peck of dragon peppers.

Smack whack crack
wham bang bonk boom!
Gob building new fancy room!

Pshkohhh...
Lower! Deeper!
Drop, drop, drop!

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Brainfruit must have
proper lockbox.

This smells like a revolution.
Is this a revolution? Can we
make it a revolution?

How dare that harlot spurn
me for a filthy commoner!

I have brought milord a
man who claims he can
be of help...for a price.

Coin is no object. I only
wish the lady returned
unharmed. As for the cur...
do with him as you see fit.
Yes, yer lordship.

Come now, you'll have
to do better than that!

If they come again,
I will handle them!
The world just keeps on spinning and spinning, kupo...
I think I'm going to be sick, kupo...

She will come to her
senses once she realizes
she has no other choice.
Of course, Milord.

Hand over the lass and
we can all go home happy.

Tell the baronet to come
here and face me himself!

We haven't the coin to
buy the mutton! If Mother
learns of this, she'll take
the switch to both of us!

I told you we shouldn't
have gotten those honey cakes!
Now what do we do...?

There's a poor girl what
weeps by the fountain
every night...
Enough! I beg of you!

Mama and Papa...
They still haven't come back.
Meep...
Have you seen Master Mogzin? He owes me kupo nuts!
Ah... That feels good...
Step outside Bahrr Lehs at your own peril, kupo!
So hot... So tired...
Come on, put your pom into it!
No, not there, not there!
Hmmm... That doesn't look right...
Does that look level to you, kupo?
So warm, kupo. It's like there's a fire in your belly.
I can just lose myself in the music, kupo!
Is it twirl, jump, twirl or twirl, twirl, jump?
Have you ever seen something so heartwarming?
I...I can't feel my pom, kupo.
I'll let you guys finish the rest.
We'll never finish at this rate.
I'm not going to make it, kupo...
Hey! Umph...wait for me, kupo!
I want to see if I can reach the top...
Didn't Mogek want us back soon?
I should've known it was too good to be true...
Revenge <cough> will be ours, kupo!
And why are we here again?

Because Rowena'd have
our heads on a shelf
selling for scrips if we weren't.
Oi! You have enough nails!?

Do I look like I need any
more nails!?
The Mogmenders are safe under our protection!
This place is quite...pleasant.
I envy the grace with which they move.
Perhaps this arrangement with the sons of man is not so bad.
To think working with dragons could be so pleasurable.
Wherever did that crate disappear to?
<mumble> <mumble>

That's not death, you fool!
It's just some passerby!

Ahhh! See!? See!?
Death stalks us
at every turn!

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Grand Sers! Grand Sers!
This is final warning!
Happy Starlight, friend! Won't you help us work miracles?
Starlight, star bright! Help us bring good cheer to the children tonight!
'Tis Starlight season! Care to help us spread happiness and joy?

Oh yes, I like me men
on their hands and knees!

You take all laudtalks for
design, I take all jinglyshine!

Yes, I suppose you cannot
spell “automaton” without
“a tomato.”

I cannot see worth a
damn in this wretched thing!

Pssst!
(I ran out of water a bell
ago...but the cropmaster
don't have to know, eh?)

Naught more stimulatin'
than watchin' pumpkins
grow, I reckon.

Calling all prospective
engineers!

Gobbie mindfruit is ripe
for bellyfilling! Come
take a bite!

Ravishing Rainlander! Crave
you succulent secrets of
automaton cogbonding?

Might someone lend me
a hand? Anyone? ANYONE!?

Higher! Taller!
Bigger! Larger!

The barony's coffers are
deep, my dear. You will
want for naught in this life.

My lord, we must straight
back. Your father will wish
to discuss the dowry.
Wait!

Begone.
The Pillars is no place
for one of your standing.

Ah, if it isn't the lowborn
wretch who fancies himself
the good lady's suitor.
Summon the constable.

You can throw me in the
darkest of oubliettes, and
cast the key to the clouds.
Our love will not fade.

But will that love fill her
belly? Will it wrap her in
the finest of Eastern silks?

I yearn not for those things
you associate with happiness...

...for without the love of
dear Peter, they would
provide mine heart little solace.

If it would please you to
see me live a lie─to look
into my dead eyes each
morn─then fine. I am yours.

But is that truly a more
lamentable fate than
looking into no eyes at all?

No. I was a fool to think
I could reason with a
woman in love.
Leave me. Both of you.
Thank you...milord.

Reginald. You know
what I must ask of you...
You should still be abed...

My next ship?
Needs to be faster.
I'll see to it, Captain!
Swifter than swift, you hear?
...Not sturdier?

Ain't no one keepin' up
with the Redbills!
Keepin' yourself in trouble?

I'm meant to be working, but...
Please don't tell Stacia!

I do not understand why,
yet I feel oddly at home here.

Right, then.
Time for a spot of plunder...
These playful movements...they intrigue me.
Tee hee hee! They can't take their eyes off me!
The most important thing is that everyone leaves happy!
Ladies and gentlemen, thank you for your patience! Let's make this a Little Ladies' Day to remember!
Encore! Encore! Encore...!
What adorable costumes!

I still pack backthoughts
of earlytimes in Idyllshire...

Overmany quillwords see
gobbiebrain abursting!

Decease and insist!
Beyond shutport lies
secrets unmeant for
uplander wide-eyes!

Come! Downsit with gob
and longpeer the seasky!

It might help if I had some
ink to go with this quill.

No longer calling all
prospective engineers!

Gobbie mindfruit tree is
plucked to barebottoms!

Oh Father, what have I done?
How am I to feed this child
on a weed-puller's wages?

You missed one! Over there!
No, not your there,
my there!
Y-Yes, milord!

I knows me a watched pot
ne'er boils, but Ma said
aught 'bout watched grapes!

A city full to burstin' with
gobbie lifts and pulleys,
yet still we has all these
bloody swivin' stairs.

You see that, uplander?
I built that! Uh...with a
little hand-lending, of course.

Welcome to the Hard Place!
Pull up a rock! Hah hah hah!

Hoo! Hah!
Hoo hoo hah!

<click> <click>
My limbs...they will not stop moving.
Won't you dance with me, kupo?
What!? I only struck 'im once!

Alright, I may have taken a
tumble or three with her
Ned...but that don't give
her the right to steal my cow!

Hmph. If he only knew his
son's true sire.

Where have you two been?
Father's fever has grown
worse and we need those
popotoes for his stew.

Forgive us, Mother...
There are no popotoes...

We used the last of the
coin on...on...honey cakes...

On honey cakes!?
ON HONEY CAKES!?

If the fever takes your
father, those cakes might
be the last thing you
ever eat!

I'll have to sell the both
of you to the goblins!
No, Mother!
Anything but that!

Then you'd best hope that
the refuse pile behind the
inn turns up something good.
Come on now!

Will someone tell me
why we are here again?

Why? Just a friendly race,
of course. You lads run,
we girls take care of the
rest.

Well then, what are we
waitin' for? I'm gonna
sprint circles around
rabbit-ears, here!

Lookin' for some action,
milord? I'll give you ten to
one on the Hyur.

Lookin' for some action,
milady? I'll give you ten to
one on the Hyur.
Ten to...what?

Ahem!
Run like you mean it,
boys. I've a moon's
allowance riding on this.
Ready...GO!

Hah hah hah! I'm the
fastest in all Dravania!

I shouldn't have sold
my breakfast to that goblin.
I was born to run!
I need...to...catch my...breath...

You cheated!
I want a rematch!

I cheated?
You cheated!

The sun's going down.
I'm going to need a bit
more light to count my
winnings.

Rain? Let's take this
inside, boys.
I'll race you to the inn!
This mountain did not fight...as a gentleman...
Oh, Inspector! Are you hurt!? Maybe you should hibernate a bit longer.
I shall see that someone pays for this! Why is my name not on here!?
Watch well, Honoroit—you may learn a thing or two!
My lord, please stop this before you hurt yourself!
One good ticket—that's all I need!
Get ready for a Raubahn roasting!
I'll have ye know the Admiral's no slouch!
I cannot help but feel at a disadvantage here...

Not even a nibble...
Just one more cast!
Ready whenever you are!

Twenty years since the
mad king's attack and yet
it is still so beautiful.

I have never seen the statue
from so close before!
The building ahead is the Closed Fist!

Only Disciples of War or Magic
may venture inside.
Fire everything!
Destroy the artillery!
For the Empire!
Was that... No, just my eyes playing tricks...
We mustn't let them escape...
Where could they have gone?
They're close...
Are you alright?
That wound looks deep...

Quickly!
Captain Wolf needs you!
Hrah!
Grah!
I'll show you!
Heh heh...
Enough!
That stings!
Just look at it!
It's so scaly...
Did it just speak!?
No telling what awaits. Stay sharp.
So, er, where do we go exactly?
Would help if there were a path.
Hm, I think this floor moves.
Let's all gather at the center.
Aha!
Let the fun begin.
Is that one of those monitors?
Shall we show our strength to it?
It's different to the ones earlier.
What's this cube, now?
I suspect we're about to find out.
Now, this is my kind of battle!
Hold on! I'm working on it!
Some kind of teleporter?
Looks like we're going through.
I'll give it a try!
I'll not fall that easily!

Were you going to bet, or
just stare at that two till
it magically becomes an ace?

Pipe down. Makin' yer
sorry arse sweat is
all part o' me strategy.
The imperials are everywhere...
Reinforcements?
I'm fine! See to the others!
It can't end here...
Come out, come out, wherever you are!
Confound it, wherever are they hiding?
They are close. I can sense it...
Was that─? Oh, that's just a tree...
H-Hey, wait!
Heh, someone's eager. Come on, let's follow.
Foolish...fool...
Not the pom...
I'm too young to kupo...
It is just as I thought.
Our worst fears are confirmed...
That leaves three...
Back to the ship!
The cargo is secure?
Hehe, I wonder what awaits.
Uh, there's more this time.
Yet another model.
Steady does it, Wedge...
Look, another teleporter!
And on we go...
Not like this...
Mercy!
Moving along like clockwork!
You know no hesitation.
Well, of course. We're mortal.
We may need to strengthen the undercarriage...
These bearings are not good enough.

Who goes there!?
Show yourselves!
What was that...?
That structure ahead must be the Deltascape.
And there're two monitors in the way...
Kill herhim!
Bah! Bloody waste o' coin!
The hells you doin'!?
Hack herhim to pieces!
Godsdammit!

Hurry up and make
herhim dead already!
Please accept this gift as thanks for your services.
What has happened here!?
Looters!?

Man-flesh is ours!
Man-flesh is ours!
Go and loot your own loots!

Eat your flesh too
for this trespass!

You don't want...
to go back there.
This'll make a fine hull.

No room.
Move along.

My pot.
Here first.

AAAHHH!!!
Don't scare me like that!
Nothing to see here.

Fortune smiles on
the wise shopper!

But of course all you
see here is authentic!

He was a damned pirate,
I tell you. He had an
eyepatch!

Where did you find that
amazing earthenware?
Might you be interested
in selling?

If I could only recall
what I was searching for...

The Sekiseigumi bastards
will be the death of us!

It feels like I'm wearing
nothing at all.

Lower...
Lower...
Loooweeer...

My, what broad
shoulders you have.

Would you like
to join us?

Go on! You can have
the first punch!

No, you can have the
first punch!

Would someone just
punch someone already?
Strength!
Honor!
Blood!

Back the way ye came,
filthy ijin.

Sandals! Get your sandals!
Guaranteed to last or your
next pair is free!

Father will kill you if he
finds out you took his
drawings of the pretty maids.

The tea here is sublime.
Not like the swill they
serve at that teahouse
across town.
